<%= render "shared/aeo_answer_block", variant: :about %>

<%# Hero Section %>
<section class="bg-navy-900 w-full">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-0 px-6 py-12 lg:px-20 lg:py-20">
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-5 lg:pr-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="bg-campaign-gold h-8 w-[3px]"></div>
        <span class="text-campaign-gold font-sans text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">About Andrew</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-white font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[52px] font-bold leading-[1.15]">
        Honest leadership.<br />Real results.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 font-sans text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
        Andrew Clough is running for Congress to bring honest, accountable, and compassionate leadership to South Carolina's 5th Congressional District.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-2">
        <%= link_to "Join the Campaign", volunteer_path, class: "bg-campaign-gold text-white font-sans text-sm font-bold px-7 py-3.5 rounded transition-colors hover:bg-campaign-gold-dark" %>
        <a href="#his-story" class="border border-white/30 text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 rounded transition-colors hover:bg-white/10">Read His Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full lg:w-[420px] bg-white/[0.06] flex items-center justify-center py-10 lg:py-0">
      <%= image_tag 'andrew-cloughA.jpg', class: "w-[280px] lg:w-[300px] h-[350px] lg:h-[380px] object-cover rounded border-2 border-campaign-gold/30" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# His Story Section %>
<section id="his-story" class="bg-white w-full">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-20 px-6 py-16 lg:px-20 lg:py-20">
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="bg-campaign-gold h-7 w-[3px]"></div>
        <span class="text-campaign-gold font-sans text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">His Story</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-3xl lg:text-[36px] font-bold leading-[1.2]">A life rooted in service</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-gray-500 font-sans text-base lg:text-lg leading-[1.75]">
        <p>Raised with deep American roots and a commitment to public service, Andrew's family traces its heritage in the United States back to 1635, embodying a legacy of hard work and perseverance.</p>
        <p>Andrew is not a career politician. He knows firsthand the challenges facing working families — working long shifts, balancing commitments, and building a life in the Carolinas. Andrew is a proud union member with American Airlines and understands the importance of protecting good jobs and expanding opportunities for all.</p>
        <p>Married to Ninfa, a long-term immigrant and mother of four — including a U.S. Army service member — Andrew's family reflects the diversity, resilience, and dreams of our community. His fight for justice and residency for his wife and family has only strengthened his resolve to advocate for fairness, opportunity, and dignity for every resident of the district.</p>
        <p>Andrew's priorities are simple: restore trust in government, deliver real results for everyday people, and build a stronger, more united future. He stands for better schools, safer neighborhoods, fair wages, and honest representation — not politics as usual.</p>
        <p>South Carolina's 5th District deserves a leader who listens, learns, and never gives up on the promise of a better tomorrow. Andrew Clough is ready to serve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full lg:w-[360px] flex flex-col gap-6">
      <blockquote class="bg-ivory-50 border-l-4 border-campaign-gold rounded-lg p-7">
        <p class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl italic leading-relaxed">"I'm not a career politician. I'm one of us — and I'm ready to fight for the people of District 5."</p>
        <cite class="block text-gray-500 font-sans text-sm font-semibold not-italic mt-4">— Andrew Clough</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <div class="bg-ivory-50 rounded-lg p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <span class="text-campaign-gold font-sans text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">Fast Facts</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-sans text-sm w-20 flex-shrink-0">Home</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-sans text-sm font-medium">Rock Hill, SC</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-sans text-sm w-20 flex-shrink-0">Party</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-sans text-sm font-medium">Democrat</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-sans text-sm w-20 flex-shrink-0">District</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-sans text-sm font-medium">SC-05</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-sans text-sm w-20 flex-shrink-0">Union</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-sans text-sm font-medium">American Airlines</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-sans text-sm w-20 flex-shrink-0">Family</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-sans text-sm font-medium">Wife Ninfa, four children</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-sans text-sm w-20 flex-shrink-0">Primary</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-sans text-sm font-medium">June 2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# Values Section %>
<section class="bg-ivory-50 w-full">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 lg:px-20 lg:py-20 flex flex-col gap-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <div class="bg-campaign-gold h-7 w-[3px]"></div>
      <span class="text-campaign-gold font-sans text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">Values</span>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-2xl font-bold">Community First</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed">Every decision Andrew makes in Congress will start with one question: does this help the people of District 5? Not donors. Not party leadership. Neighbors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-2xl font-bold">Straight Talk</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed">Andrew says what he means. No hedging, no spin. If he disagrees with something, he'll say so. District 5 has had enough of politicians who talk around every answer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-2xl font-bold">Show Up</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed">Being a congressman means being present. Town halls, school visits, coffee meetups — Andrew will be in the district regularly, not just at election time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# CTA Section %>
<section class="bg-navy-900 w-full">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 px-6 py-16 lg:px-20 lg:py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 max-w-lg">
      <span class="text-campaign-gold font-sans text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">Get Involved</span>
      <h2 class="text-white font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[36px] font-bold leading-[1.2]">This campaign runs on neighbors, not donors.</h2>
      <p class="text-white/65 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed">Door knocking, phone banking, hosting a coffee — every hour you give makes a real difference in a district this competitive. Andrew needs you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row lg:flex-col gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
      <%= link_to "Volunteer Now", volunteer_path, class: "bg-campaign-gold text-white font-sans text-sm font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded text-center transition-colors hover:bg-campaign-gold-dark" %>
      <a href="https://secure.actblue.com/donate/andrew-clough-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="border border-white/30 text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded text-center transition-colors hover:bg-white/10">Donate</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
